elements.name: As an admin I want to add a delet a Page

I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having css selector "#ember10"
I click on element having css selector "#ember12 > span"
I click on element having css selector "a[href='#/editor/page/']"
I click on element having css selector "div.gh-koenig-editor-pane textarea.gh-editor-title"
I enter "Page_1" into input field having css selector "div.gh-koenig-editor-pane textarea.gh-editor-title"
I click on element having css selector "span.fw4.midgrey-l2"
I click on element having css selector "header.gh-editor-header div > div > a"
I click on element having css selector "li.gh-list-row.gh-posts-list-item"
I click on element having css selector "button.post-settings"
